room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rockford in Rockford
room_description: Your archaeological team’s quest is to unlock the secrets of the Pharaoh’s Tomb. Other teams have attempted and vanished during their search. The Ancient Egyptians were known for their mystical ways, opulence, and power.  Upon the death of a pharaoh, the corpse was enclosed inside a sarcophagus, with provisions for the afterlife. Work together with your team to find the tomb and escape.
